local Manager = s_WordDictionaryDatabase; Manager.allwords["hieroglyph"]={"hieroglyph","['haɪ(ə)rəglɪf]","['haɪərəɡlɪf]","n.象形文字",'n.象形文字,图画文字,秘密文字','||Hieroglyphs|| are symbols in the form of pictures, which are used in some writing systems, especially those of ancient Egypt.','象形文字是以图像为形式的符号，它被用于一些书写体系中，特别是古埃及。','Pierre knew very well what a hieroglyph was, but he did not venture to say so.','皮埃尔十分清楚地知道，“象形符号”指的是什么，但是他不敢说话。'}
